Dialogue.text: Good morning, Sector 7! Today is the Jeha {current_day}, bringing a several dozen one day closer to their once-in-a-lifetime trip from the overlord (all hail Overlord Aso).

Dialogue526.text: Breaking news: scientists think they may have found the cause for the CX-6 virus.

Dialogue535.text: The first infections have been linked back to the exotic pet, rapos.

Dialogue549.text: Cute furry pet or death sentence? Why not both!
